    <data key="d0">SBB Cargo: Data Collection and Processing with Serverless Analytics Services</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4-teOQ_dJvY</data>
    <data key="d2">Low-maintenance serverless digital twin architecture. Filters high-volume IoT data (3M messages/day per train) down to critical indicators using Kinesis Analytics before storing in DynamoDB.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
